Charles Trask is the son of Cyrus Trask and the half-brother of Adam. Charles is a violent, cynical, manipulative man who works his fatherâ€™s farm and greedily amasses a large fortune. Although Charles is deeply jealous of his brother, he also needs Adam and misses him terribly when he is not at home. Charles plays the Cain role in the first generation of the Trasks. He is one of the only characters capable of inspiring fear in the thoroughly evil Cathy Ames.